### 2. GET `/api/model-result/:sessionId`

Poll for the CNN prediction. Frontend polls every 2 s for up to 40 s **in the background while games run**.

**Response 200 — processing:**
```json
{ "session_id": "srv-a1b2c3d4", "status": "processing", "predictions": null }
```

**Response 200 — done:**
```json
{
  "session_id": "srv-a1b2c3d4",
  "status": "done",
  "model_version": "retinasafe-cnn-v2.1",
  "processed_at": "2025-09-14T10:23:41Z",
  "predictions": {
    "diabetic_retinopathy": { "probability": 0.74, "risk_level": "High" },
    "macular_degeneration": { "probability": 0.22, "risk_level": "Low" },
    "glaucoma":             { "probability": 0.48, "risk_level": "Moderate" },
    "cataract":             { "probability": 0.31, "risk_level": "Low" }
  }
}
```

**Risk level thresholds (model output):**

| probability | risk_level |
|---|---|
| < 0.35 | Low |
| 0.35–0.64 | Moderate |
| ≥ 0.65 | High |

**Errors:** `404` unknown session · `500` inference failed (frontend proceeds game-only)

