## Frontend File Reference

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `session.js` | Session state (localStorage). Survives page navigation between games. |
| `api-bridge.js` | All API calls. Full mock mode for frontend dev without a backend. |
| `game-collector.js` | Add to every game page. Call `RetinaSafeCollector.submit(payload)` to save + redirect. |
| `screening.js` | 4-step wizard controller. |
| `nav.js` | Shared nav bar injected into every page. |

